Tasks June 23:

Functions:

#function to add two numbers
'''
#My Solution:

#First get two input

n1 = int(input("Give your 1St number: "))
n2 = int(input("Give youer 2nd number:"))

#here my function
def add(val1,val2):     #function fuction_name (arugments)
    val = val1 + val2   #In inside adding  values
    return val          #return the function value
print(add(n1,n2))       #print the function values

